{"tid":1432999,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何韻詩養貓有雷射筆：拉我啊笨","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:20:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58263591860aaaaca3fdfcd24446a0ce9ccb34a0","tid":1432999,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190808/20744979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F20744979&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO76gSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=a343e41a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F20744979&h=6953ee8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190808/20744979</a><br />\n<br />\n何韻詩養貓有雷射筆：拉我啊笨<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190808/large/1565185755_797c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565185755_797c.jpg&h=1f27afdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸會大學學生會會長方仲賢前晚在深水埗買觀星筆後，被便衣警員截查，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器拘捕，事件令社會震驚，多位藝人也紛紛在社交網怒斥警方執法不當。<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩爆Seed怒轟警方：<br />\n「聽日就全民一齊一人買一支雷射筆，睇你捉得幾多個。」阿詩指屋企有五隻貓，揚言會買夠五支：「貓與laser是好朋友這是常識，我𠵱家屋企就有一支，犯法啊拉我啊笨。」阿詩還連環出post寸警方：「其實鑊鏟、煎pan都可以成為攻擊性武器㗎，不如禁埋全港九新界師奶去街市買嘢啦。」最後還hashtag斥警察「目中無法」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190808/large/1565185754_b8ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565185754_b8ae.jpg&h=e3bd5d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王喜：<br />\n「如果呢款觀星筆係攻擊性武器，咁你應該拉晒販賣攻擊性武器嘅舖頭先啱喎，係咪？」他又指出：「賣藤條嗰啲舖頭同買入持有藤條嗰啲人又使唔使拉呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190808/large/1565185756_743e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565185756_743e.jpg&h=cc90102e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n空手道黑帶的歐錦棠：<br />\n「建議所有空手道黑帶全部自首。黑帶係人間凶器。」他又寸爆克警濫權，表示：「師傅，為咗我嘅幸福着想，我求你搣我柴啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190808/large/1565185754_6f46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565185754_6f46.jpg&h=6f6bb53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林日曦：<br />\n「𡃁仔買電筒要拉，𡃁妹喺街收拾垃圾要拉，見男嘅就叉頸，見女嘅就搞到人走光，亂開槍，亂棍毆，有cam影住都咁，冇cam影住時不堪設想。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190808/large/1565185755_4528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565185755_4528.jpg&h=de22838b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎瑞恩指買激光筆的用途大家心知：<br />\n「為確證雷射筆安全可靠，試吓射完佢（方仲賢）雙眼，通過安全標準嘅話，要求警方要立即放人兼道歉！」有人指小恩子盲撐，她說：「咁都盲撐？如果證實安全，我要求警方道歉喎！」  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n怕秋後算賬港片撤回"},{"pid":"8d7597736e1aa42decae7a89090c146434aeb4c5","tid":1432999,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歐錦棠大師兄"}]}